Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DRAGON KNIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw it away to give you time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can lift a rock, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dragon scales are as hard as steel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to target its faces!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Earth Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even its faces are like steel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,His sword wore down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't win, fighting them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For this, I'll take them all out\Nwith a single huge spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty spirits asleep in the earth,\NI now ask you to hear my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Betan!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I guess that's a spell straight from\NGrand Sorcerer Matorif for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it used up all of my Magic Power\Nin the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&} {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With puny spells like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Give that to the boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, sorry! You've got to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Run?! How can we run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bunch of cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That crest! It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the mark!\NWe've got the advantage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, that crest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Dragon Knight in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's even more intense than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Dai! That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! He's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why is everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you're not human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeing your inhuman fighting abilities\Nhas terrified them all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humans can be so selfish.\NAnd after you protected their city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My rather insulting friends\Ncall me "The Reaper."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban, The Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the Dragon Legion Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that distinguished.\NI'm just a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army has been abuzz,\Nspeculating on your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was lent some Dragons from the\NDragon Legion and was sent to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, I was able to see\Nwhat you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, also, the real Dragon Legion\NCommander will probably show up soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to lure you into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by... my identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. You called Dai\N"the Dragon Knight," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be the Dragon Knight from the\Nlegends of our homeland, Teran Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The Dragon Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Teran? And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Nabara the Seer.\NAnd this is my granddaughter, Meruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a country north of Bengana.\NIt's called the Mystic Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Mystic Country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I go there...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sovereign Rock Castle's\Nfootprints end here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Field of Death...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban's Dark Army\Nmust be positioned there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army drove\Nmy homeland of Carl to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taking down Carl\Ncouldn't have been an easy task.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which Legion did it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Teran Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's kind of shabby.\NIt's more of a village than a kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, but, you know, I'm glad\Nthe Dark Army hasn't attacked this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To be blunt, it's because\Nit has no tactical value.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Teran is a kingdom in name only.\NIt has no military power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of his love for nature\Nand devotion to the gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the king forbade development\Nof weapons and items.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they would bring disaster upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But that also weakened the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody prefers\Na life filled with luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The population moved to other countries,\Nand this country was left to rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there are only about 50 people.\NOf course, we were among those who left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I still love this quiet homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Nabara, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find something\Nthat will tell me who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. What are you\Ngetting worked up about, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have to know! Just who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about decrepit. Is this some ruin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the Dragon Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the mark\Nthat appears on my forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Teran worships the God of Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And this crest is revered and feared\Nas a sign of the God of Dragons' power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He who bears this crest\Non his forehead is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of human is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be human at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We believe it is a servant of the gods.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to legends,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Dragon Knight wields awesome power,\Ncan cast any spell,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and, with the heavens, earth, and sea\Nas its allies, will destroy all creation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of being destroys all creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be our savior or our destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only written that it wields power\Nlike a rebirth of the God of Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a forbidden temple\Nat the bottom of this lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul of the God of Dragons\Nis said to rest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. If you really do have something\Nto do with the Dragon Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps you can enter that temple\Nand find some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... going down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An underwater temple, huh? Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... shouldn't we all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I want to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. At least take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it in Bengana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never wondered who I am before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I washed up on Dermline Island\Nas a baby and was raised among monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa Burasu scolded me a lot,\Nbut he cared for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The monsters never excluded me\Njust because I wasn't a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But humans won't accept me\Nunless I'm also a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you or Leona to hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Worrying about things that don't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were friends!\NI thought we were companions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're a monster or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That... never mattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Dragon Temple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do I get inside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's air in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who goes there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Name yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A talking crystal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Dragon Crystal.\NGuardian of this temple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know!\NAm I really a Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you ask this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhere I was born or who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are the Dragon Knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This temple cannot be entered\Nby anyone but the Dragon Knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your presence here is proof itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is a Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a human or a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is neither.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three gods created this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The God of Dragons, the God of Darklings,\Nand the God of Humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dragon Knight is the ultimate creature\Ncreated by those three gods.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Created?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. Long ago,\Nby three great celestial beings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why create such a creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone else has entered this temple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is impossible. The Dragon Knight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Legion Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he's the Dragon Legion Commander.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the real deal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there's something about him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man is also a Dragon Knight?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible. Two Dragon Knights\Nexisting in the same age...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Crystal must have already\Ntold you that you're a Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if it did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I want your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we shall destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the human world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran, the Dragon Legion Commander\Nreveals the Dragon Knight's mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For Dai, who seeks to defeat\Nthe Dark King, it is a cruel revelation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai resists, using his Aban Strash,\Nbut it has no effect on Baran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran then reveals a shocking truth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dragon Master General Baran"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
